---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { sources, timelineByEra } from '../../../data/timeline';
---

<Layout title="Battle Story" description="Conoce el Battle Story de Zoids: la narrativa que conecta los model kits con décadas de guerras en el Planeta Zi.">
	<a href="/archivo/" class="back-btn">← Volver al Archivo</a>

	<section class="bs-hero">
		<h1 class="bs-title">Battle Story</h1>
		<p class="bs-subtitle">La historia detrás de los model kits</p>
	</section>

	<section class="bs-intro">
		<p>El <strong>Battle Story</strong> es la narrativa oficial que acompaña a los modelos de Zoids desde 1983. A diferencia de los animes, que cuentan historias independientes, la Battle Story es una saga continua que conecta cada kit lanzado por TOMY con las guerras en el Planeta Zi.</p>
		<p>La historia se contaba a través de las cajas de los Zoids, manuales de instrucciones, libros complementarios como los <em>Zoids Battle Story</em> de Shogakukan, revistas como <em>Dengeki Hobby</em>, y publicaciones oficiales como los <em>Fan Books</em>. Cada nuevo Zoid lanzado al mercado tenía un papel en la narrativa: su origen, su primer despliegue en batalla y su impacto en la guerra.</p>
		<p>La Battle Story abarca miles de años de historia, desde la formación del Planeta Zi y la evolución de las primeras formas de vida metálicas, pasando por las guerras entre la <strong>República de Helic</strong> y el <strong>Imperio de Zenebas</strong>, la intervención del <strong>Imperio de Guylos</strong>, la devastadora <strong>Gran Catástrofe</strong>, hasta el surgimiento del <strong>Imperio de Neo Zenebas</strong> y las batallas del futuro lejano.</p>
		<p>Es una historia de guerra, política, traición y tecnología — contada modelo a modelo durante décadas y que aún sigue en desarrollo.</p>
	</section>

	<section class="timeline-section">
		<h2 class="timeline-heading">Línea del Tiempo</h2>
		<p class="timeline-note">Todas las fechas están en el calendario de Planet Zi, "ZAC" (Zi Anno Civitas).</p>

		<nav class="era-nav">
			{timelineByEra.map((era) => (
				<a href={`#era-${era.era}`} class="era-nav-item" style={`--era-color: ${era.color}`}>
					<span class="era-nav-dot"></span>
					<span class="era-nav-label">{era.label} <span class="era-nav-range">({era.yearRange})</span></span>
				</a>
			))}
		</nav>

		<div class="timeline">
			{timelineByEra.map((era) => (
				<>
					<div class="era-separator" id={`era-${era.era}`} style={`--era-color: ${era.color}`}>
						<div class="era-separator-line"></div>
						<div class="era-separator-content">
							<h3 class="era-separator-title">{era.label}</h3>
						</div>
						<div class="era-separator-line"></div>
					</div>

					{era.events.map((event, i) => (
						<div class={`timeline-item ${i % 2 === 0 ? 'timeline-item--left' : 'timeline-item--right'}`} style={`--era-color: ${era.color}`}>
							<div class="timeline-dot"></div>
							<div class="timeline-content">
								<span class="timeline-date">{event.date}</span>
								<h4 class="timeline-event-title">{event.title}</h4>
								<p class="timeline-event-desc">{event.description}</p>
								{event.newZoids && event.newZoids.length > 0 && (
									<div class="timeline-zoids">
										<span class="timeline-zoids-label">Zoids destacados:</span>
										{event.newZoids.map((z) => (
											<span class="timeline-zoid-tag">{z}</span>
										))}
									</div>
								)}
							</div>
						</div>
					))}
				</>
			))}
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="credits">
		<h2 class="credits-title">Créditos</h2>
		<p class="credits-text">Esta línea del tiempo está basada en el trabajo de <strong>Falcarius</strong>, publicada originalmente en <a href="http://zoidsathenaeum.890m.com/databanks/timeline.htm" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Zoids Athenaeum</a>. Traducida y adaptada al español por The Core Zi.</p>

		<details class="sources-details">
			<summary class="sources-summary">Ver fuentes originales</summary>
			<ul class="sources-list">
				{sources.map((s) => (
					<li><strong>{s.code}</strong> — {s.description}</li>
				))}
			</ul>
		</details>
	</section>
</Layout>

<style>
	.back-btn {
		display: inline-block;
		background: var(--color-surface);
		border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
		border-radius: 8px;
		box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
		color: var(--color-text);
		font-family: 'Russo One', sans-serif;
		font-size: 0.85rem;
		padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
		text-decoration: none;
		transition: background-color 0.2s, border-color 0.2s, color 0.2s;
	}

	.back-btn:hover {
		background: var(--color-accent);
		border-color: var(--color-accent);
		color: var(--color-bg);
	}

	/* Hero */
	.bs-hero {
		text-align: center;
		padding: 3rem 1rem 1rem;
	}

	.bs-title {
		font-family: 'Russo One', sans-serif;
		font-size: 3rem;
		color: var(--color-accent);
		margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
	}

	.bs-subtitle {
		font-family: 'Russo One', sans-serif;
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		color: var(--color-text-muted);
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.1em;
	}

	/* Intro */
	.bs-intro {
		max-width: 750px;
		margin: 2rem auto 0;
	}

	.bs-intro p {
		color: var(--color-text-muted);
		font-size: 1rem;
		line-height: 1.7;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.bs-intro strong {
		color: var(--color-text);
	}

	.bs-intro em {
		color: var(--color-accent);
		font-style: italic;
	}

	/* Timeline section */
	.timeline-section {
		margin-top: 4rem;
	}

	.timeline-heading {
		font-family: 'Russo One', sans-serif;
		font-size: 2rem;
		color: var(--color-accent);
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
		position: relative;
		padding-bottom: 0.75rem;
	}

	.timeline-heading::after {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		bottom: 0;
		left: 50%;
		transform: translateX(-50%);
		width: 80px;
		height: 3px;
		background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--color-accent), transparent);
		border-radius: 2px;
	}

	.timeline-note {
		color: var(--color-text-muted);
		font-size: 0.85rem;
		font-style: italic;
		opacity: 0.7;
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	/* Era navigation */
	.era-nav {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: center;
		gap: 1.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
	}

	.era-nav-item {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 0.5rem;
		text-decoration: none;
		color: var(--color-text-muted);
		font-size: 0.85rem;
		transition: color 0.2s;
	}

	.era-nav-item:hover {
		color: var(--color-text);
	}

	.era-nav-dot {
		width: 10px;
		height: 10px;
		border-radius: 50%;
		background: var(--era-color);
		flex-shrink: 0;
	}

	.era-nav-range {
		opacity: 0.6;
		font-size: 0.75rem;
	}

	/* Timeline */
	.timeline {
		position: relative;
		max-width: 900px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 0 1rem;
	}

	.timeline::before {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		left: 50%;
		transform: translateX(-50%);
		top: 0;
		bottom: 0;
		width: 2px;
		background: var(--color-text-muted);
		opacity: 0.2;
	}

	/* Era separator */
	.era-separator {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 1.5rem;
		margin: 3rem 0 2rem;
		position: relative;
		z-index: 1;
		scroll-margin-top: 100px;
	}

	.era-separator:first-child {
		margin-top: 0;
	}

	.era-separator-line {
		flex: 1;
		height: 2px;
		background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--era-color), transparent);
	}

	.era-separator-content {
		text-align: center;
		flex-shrink: 0;
	}

	.era-separator-title {
		font-family: 'Russo One', sans-serif;
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		color: var(--era-color);
		margin-bottom: 0.15rem;
	}

	.era-separator-range {
		font-size: 0.8rem;
		color: var(--color-text-muted);
	}

	/* Timeline items */
	.timeline-item {
		position: relative;
		width: 50%;
		padding: 0 2.5rem 2rem;
	}

	.timeline-item--left {
		left: 0;
		padding-right: 2.5rem;
		text-align: right;
	}

	.timeline-item--right {
		left: 50%;
		padding-left: 2.5rem;
		text-align: left;
	}

	.timeline-dot {
		position: absolute;
		top: 0.5rem;
		width: 12px;
		height: 12px;
		border-radius: 50%;
		background: var(--era-color);
		border: 2px solid var(--color-bg);
		z-index: 2;
	}

	.timeline-item--left .timeline-dot {
		right: -6px;
	}

	.timeline-item--right .timeline-dot {
		left: -6px;
	}

	.timeline-content {
		background: var(--color-surface);
		border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
		border-radius: 12px;
		padding: 1.25rem;
		transition: border-color 0.2s;
	}

	.timeline-content:hover {
		border-color: var(--era-color);
	}

	.timeline-date {
		display: inline-block;
		background: var(--era-color);
		color: #000;
		font-family: 'Russo One', sans-serif;
		font-size: 0.7rem;
		padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem;
		border-radius: 4px;
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
		letter-spacing: 0.03em;
	}

	.timeline-event-title {
		font-family: 'Russo One', sans-serif;
		font-size: 1rem;
		color: var(--color-text);
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}

	.timeline-event-desc {
		color: var(--color-text-muted);
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	.timeline-zoids {
		margin-top: 0.75rem;
		display: flex;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		gap: 0.35rem;
		align-items: center;
	}

	.timeline-item--left .timeline-zoids {
		justify-content: flex-end;
	}

	.timeline-zoids-label {
		font-size: 0.75rem;
		color: var(--color-text-muted);
		font-weight: 600;
	}

	.timeline-zoid-tag {
		font-size: 0.7rem;
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
		color: var(--color-text);
		padding: 0.15rem 0.5rem;
		border-radius: 4px;
		border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
	}

	/* Credits */
	.credits {
		max-width: 700px;
		margin: 4rem auto 0;
		text-align: center;
		padding: 2rem;
		background: var(--color-surface);
		border-radius: 16px;
		border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
	}

	.credits-title {
		font-family: 'Russo One', sans-serif;
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		color: var(--color-accent);
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.credits-text {
		color: var(--color-text-muted);
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		line-height: 1.6;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.credits-text a {
		color: var(--color-accent);
		text-decoration: none;
	}

	.credits-text a:hover {
		text-decoration: underline;
	}

	.sources-details {
		text-align: left;
	}

	.sources-summary {
		color: var(--color-accent);
		cursor: pointer;
		font-family: 'Russo One', sans-serif;
		font-size: 0.85rem;
		text-align: center;
		padding: 0.5rem;
		transition: color 0.2s;
	}

	.sources-summary:hover {
		color: var(--color-text);
	}

	.sources-list {
		list-style: none;
		margin-top: 1rem;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 0.5rem;
	}

	.sources-list li {
		color: var(--color-text-muted);
		font-size: 0.8rem;
		line-height: 1.4;
		padding: 0.5rem 0.75rem;
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
		border-radius: 6px;
	}

	.sources-list li strong {
		color: var(--color-text);
	}

	/* Mobile */
	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.bs-hero {
			padding: 2rem 1rem 0.5rem;
		}

		.bs-title {
			font-size: 2rem;
		}

		.bs-intro {
			margin-top: 1.5rem;
		}

		.timeline-section {
			margin-top: 2rem;
		}

		.timeline-heading {
			font-size: 1.5rem;
		}

		.era-nav {
			gap: 0.75rem;
		}

		.era-nav-item {
			font-size: 0.75rem;
		}

		.timeline::before {
			left: 20px;
			transform: none;
		}

		.timeline-item,
		.timeline-item--left,
		.timeline-item--right {
			width: 100%;
			left: 0;
			padding: 0 0 1.5rem 50px;
			text-align: left;
		}

		.timeline-item--left .timeline-dot,
		.timeline-item--right .timeline-dot {
			left: 14px;
			right: auto;
		}

		.timeline-item--left .timeline-zoids {
			justify-content: flex-start;
		}

		.era-separator {
			margin: 2rem 0 1.5rem;
			padding-left: 50px;
		}

		.era-separator-line:first-child {
			display: none;
		}

		.era-separator-content {
			text-align: left;
		}

		.timeline-content {
			padding: 1rem;
		}

		.credits {
			margin-top: 2rem;
			padding: 1.5rem 1rem;
		}
	}
</style>
